{"tid":2020141,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[月經文] 好心一早放開我 從頭努力也坎坷","createTime":"2020-05-16T21:00:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T19:42:40.000Z","uid":202488,"like":22,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"12bc54a4ab5bd2faece6002ba0aa44c5c99bda29","tid":2020141,"uid":202488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T21:00:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早幾日有個ex 突然之間 ig 搵我 ，不知不覺傾翻計<br />\n啲Friend 知道咗先話我聽 佢之前仲有問我嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好心煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自問放低咗半年以上 <br />\n冇聯繫 感情淡咗<br />\n<br />\n既然仲想一齊 點解當初要咁對我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我苦夠了先搵我<br />\n「好心一早放開我 從頭努力也坎坷」<br />\n<br />\n佢約我同埋2個大學同學一齊下星期去食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點搞去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去 俾個機會大家<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不了<br />\n<br />\n利申: 絲 (借同事AC) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37a98fdf956104d093a18c2534adacacd34573fd","tid":2020141,"uid":202488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T21:01:14.000Z","msg":"好驚再面對佢<br />\n覺得經過嗰段感情好多野都卻步，唔識點同中意嘅男仔溝通，好多野都要諗過度過，好大壓力 (以前唔係咁）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85970263a60fbf03ea7af7b4a73fb3b1c27d5839","tid":2020141,"uid":202488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T21:01:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d74c86dea300243a2e816a0cf50230e16ce139f7","tid":2020141,"uid":202488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T21:03:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f08a11bc735bc350ed5bc45fe0f6218c84d8bbba","tid":2020141,"uid":202488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T21:03:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfa0e07897034acfa85dd341b889815dd315187b","tid":2020141,"uid":202488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T21:04:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6863b98e5b28780d2c48fa2426a3d1fdba0a8d5f","tid":2020141,"uid":113147,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T21:16:18.000Z","msg":"我覺得，假如你唔係一個十全十美既人，一個男仔隔左段時間搵你，係真係因為好愛你（好多人會勤佢放手，同佢講出面大把女仔等等）。同為男仔，我覺得你或者應該比個機會佢，同佢相處下先，假如無改善都可以做返朋友，經歷過第二次相處，大家都會更易放得低，而你可以好平靜咁話返比佢知無感覺了，咁樣對一個愛自己既人傷害最小。"},{"pid":"23944c5cdc6a2c151f4b96bb13f9bc03c4508fd2","tid":2020141,"uid":332751,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20